Author: Kagi
Title: [ANN] [PRE-ICO] Touchtrader - From intuition to trade with the swipe of a finger
Body: Dear participants of TouchTrader project,  Thank you for your interest in the TouchTrader project, we hope you found it interesting so far.  Unfortunately, due to some regulation concerns from some investors, flaws in our overall team structure and legal advisory we have to  suspend our ICO for undetermined time. We are not cancelling our project, but we do need time to solve these issues before moving to greater steps.  TouchTrader project is still moving forward! Stay with us for more news! All bounty participants will receive their reward after we relaunch ICO.  Our support remain active and if you have any questions please go to webmaster@touchtrader.io or info@touchtrader.io.  Kind regards, TouchTrader Team
